<%# app/views/booking_mailer/reminder.text.erb %>
Your Stay is Almost Here!
==========================

Dear <%= @booking.guest_name %>,

We're looking forward to welcoming you to The Anchorpoint Retreat in just a few days!

UPCOMING STAY
-------------
Confirmation: <%= @booking.confirmation_number %>
Check-in:     <%= @booking.check_in.strftime("%A, %B %d, %Y") %>
Check-out:    <%= @booking.check_out.strftime("%A, %B %d, %Y") %>

QUICK REMINDERS
---------------
Check-in:  <%= @property.check_in_time %>
Check-out: <%= @property.check_out_time %>
Address:   <%= @property.address %>, <%= @property.city %>, <%= @property.state %>

If you need anything before your arrival, please don't hesitate to reach out.

Safe travels!

Warm regards,
The Anchorpoint Retreat Team

---
This email was sent to <%= @booking.guest_email %>.
